Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has become a superhuman society,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.35,0:00:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and about 80% of the world's population\Nnow has some kind of special trait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world swirling with chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the profession that everyone\Nonce dreamed about and admired
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,came into the limelight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes of justice fighting villains\Nand saving people from distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is the story of\Nhow I became the greatest hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, sorry for the long wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stage that was frozen in the second match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is finally dry, so on to the next match!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The assassin from Class B!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty things have thorns, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the hero course, it's Ibara Shiozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Versus--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sparking Killing Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the hero course, it's Denki Kaminari!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Battle on, Challengers!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we'll have a super\Nflashy battle this time too--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse the interruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "assassin"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have only come to find victory,\Nnot to take my opponent's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, I wished to enter\NU.A. High School not for wicked reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for the salvation of others...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for your understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class B has people like this in it, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got big eyes and a pretty face,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like she's really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta discharge\Nall my electricity here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, she's pretty,\Nbut she's also kinda cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta ask her out sometime, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, start!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this is over, wanna grab a bite to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll comfort you if you'll have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause this match'll\Nprobably be over in a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indiscriminate Shock...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1.3 Million Volts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was decided in an instant!\NI'll say it once more! An instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiozaki advances to the second round!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was able to make the\Nmost of the opportunity I was given.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:31.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ibara Shiozaki"\N"Quirk: Vines"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ibara Shiozaki. Quirk: Vines!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The vines on her head are extendable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're detachable, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as she makes sure\Nto get plenty of water and sunlight,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll grow in almost immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, she can't go bald!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Shiozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Didn't he say\Nhe'd settle this in a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange, he was\N{\i1}defeated{\i0} in a second, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class A is supposed to be better\Nthan Class B, so isn't that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamui, Kamui!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't she be good as a sidekick?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I wish I could've gotten a better look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems straight-laced, but she's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard to deal with Shiozaki's\Nability to detach her vines, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The vines were able not only to defend\Nbut also to act as an electrical ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no way he'd shock her with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then she extended her vines to bind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaminari's Quirk was completely blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some Quirks don't work well against others,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it would've been better\Nif he'd been able to deal with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaminari's Quirk is supposed to be strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Shiozaki is a strong opponent\Nwho placed fourth in the entrance exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"mutter mutter mutter"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vines, huh? I wonder\Nif it's like Kamui Woods's Quirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Binding types really are strong.\NI hardly ever see anyone break out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be impossible to get close\Nwhile avoiding all those vines,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you'd either have to tear them off\Nor get through with brute force...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but in order to keep you from doing that,\Nshe'd go after your hands first...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:09.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"mutter mutter mutter"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just finished, but you're already\Nthinking about countermeasures, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! It's just, I mean,\Nthis is pretty much my hobby...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not every day I get a chance to see\Namazing Quirks outside of those in our class...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! I've been putting these\Ntogether for everyone in Class A, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For your Zero Gravity, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deku, you've been amazing since I met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the sports festival is making me\Nthink that you're amazing all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's time for the fourth match!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just gonna keep rolling along!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rush headlong toward the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like he's the epitome\Nof the middle of the pack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the hero course, it's Tenya Iida!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Versus--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fully-equipped with support items!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the support course, it's Mei Hatsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's up against the support course, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of fight it'll be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, what {\i1}is{\i0} that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iida's also fully-equipped with support items!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's generally against the rules\Nfor those in the hero course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who must use equipment\Nneeded to petition beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama also wore a belt,\Nso I thought it was fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He submitted a petition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I humbly apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, my heart was moved\Nby my opponent's sportsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she is from the support course,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she said she wanted an even\Nmatch since she made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wanted to fight fairly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, she gave me this equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not think I could\Nignore her fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if they both agree on it,\Nthen it's within regulations... I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:01.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hero Analysis for the Future"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Hatsume someone who'd say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since permission's been granted,\Nlet's start the fourth match!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that acceleration wonderful, Iida?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's wearing speakers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't your legs feel lighter than usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's only to be expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those leg parts are helping\Nthe wearer's movements along!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can evade easily with\Nmy hydraulic attachments!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The support companies are sitting...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're biting! I've got 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:54.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mei Hatsume"\N"Quirk: Zoom"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Hatsume. Quirk: Zoom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she gets serious, she can see\Nclearly up to five kilometer's away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I've got sensors in every direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can even deal with attacks from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iida changed course adeptly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to the auto-balancer that I made!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The leg parts detect the wearer's\Nbrainwaves to predict their movements,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:21.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--She's very good at hard selling...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The leg parts detect the wearer's\Nbrainwaves to predict their movements,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so there's no need to worry about time lag!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The auto-balancer is equipped\Nwith a 32-axis gyro sensor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be sure to keep the wearer\Nfrom falling unless the wearer wants to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you going to fight fairly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of this lightness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These electro shoes use\Nelectromagnetic induction on both feet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to allow for instant evasive action!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get her when she lands!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A capture gun to use against villains.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The capture nets are in cartridges,\Nand you can fire up to five before reloading!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who developed all of these items?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was me, Mei Hatsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone from the support companies,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the choice is clear--Mei Hatsume,\NMei Hatsume, Mei Hatsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she, a politician?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, I will talk\Nabout the next support item!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still more?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ten Minutes Later"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've presented each and every last one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing left to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The End"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hatsume is out of bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iida advances to the second round!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I used you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iida's earnest, so she probably said some things
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that sounded good to get him on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatsume's not just honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she will also use any means to reach her goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna keep right\Non going with the fifth match!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he's wearing\Na belt, he won't transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the hero course, it's Yuga Aoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bonjour.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Versus--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something going to\Ncome out of those horns? Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the hero course, it's Mina Ashido!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My first match is a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return those words right back at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mina, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama, get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat her like in those fighting games\Nwhere their clothes get ripped off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, scum?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A match between Aoyama and Ashido.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering their Quirks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama will probably attack\Nfrom a distance with his laser.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the match will be decided by how well Ashido can slip
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,through Aoyama's attacks and turn it into a close combat match.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's nothing\Nto use as cover on the stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so Ashido might be at a slight disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, why don't we get moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifth match, start!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The early bird gets the worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we were on the\Nsame team for combat training,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all about your Quirk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just one thing that's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the fitness test--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I shoot for more than a second,\NI get a stomachache.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... My stomach...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, my precious belt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama has fainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashido advances to the second round!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama's knocked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashido's easy victory is indisputable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mina's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only Aoyama and\NAshido's Quirks were switched...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too much of a scumbag.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The match unfolded as I expected,\Nbut I misjudged Ashido's physical strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even during the Quirk assessment test,\Nshe placed ninth out of everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,including the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't because of her Quirk--she's\Ngot excellent physical abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we've got no time to lose!\NLet's move on to the sixth match!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I said get back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Offense and defense in one body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dark samurai accompanied by Dark Shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the hero course, it's Fumikage Tokoyami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Versus--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All-purpose Creation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was admitted through recommendations,\Nso her abilities are certified!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the hero course, it's Momo Yaoyorozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Midoriya, what do you think of this match?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think time will be the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as Mr. Present Mic says,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm up against Tokoyami with Dark Shadow,\Noffense and defense in one body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, Tokoyami can bring\Nout Dark Shadow with no time lag,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so there is no doubt he will\Nstart with a preemptive strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I create a simple shield that doesn't take\Nmuch time and block Tokoyami's attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I just give myself enough\Ntime to make a weapon--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sixth match, start!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Dark Shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly create a shield--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, a weapon--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't collect my thoughts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His attacks have stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaoyorozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of bounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokoyami advances to the second round!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An overwhelming victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A completely overwhelming victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:16:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokoyami's Dark Shadow!\NCould it be the greatest Quirk ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokoyami's too amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he forced her out of bounds
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just by focusing his attacks\Non the shield Yaoyozoru made.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was trying not to hurt her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how easy it was for him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must feel really frustrated...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's move on! Next up--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seventh match is a\Nmatch-up between redundant Quirks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:40.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Eijiro Kirishima"    "Tetsutetsu Tetsutetsu"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manly and passionate steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the hero course,\Nit's Tetsutetsu Tetsutetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Versus--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manly and passionate hardening!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the hero course, it's Eijiro Kirishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even our intros are the same?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Tetsutetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Win like Ibara did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start this passionate seventh match!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Player Waiting Room 2"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Iida.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Urarak--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not like yourself at all!\NYour brow's all wrinkled!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just my nerves...\NMust've reached my brow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up against that Bakugo, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, after seeing\Na match like yours, Iida...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uraraka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You don't want\Nto watch the others' matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most ended quickly, and now Kirishima\Nis up against someone from Class B.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That didn't hurt at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That didn't hurt, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, next... soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, well, I don't think even Bakugo\Nwould use a full-strength explosion on a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He would.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's trying to become number one\Nto make their dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:39.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Player Waiting Room 1"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's not Kacchan,\Nno one would think about holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've helped me so much, Uraraka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I thought maybe\NI could help you a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A plan to use your Quirk against Kacchan--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rough, but I came up with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, isn't that great, Uraraka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Deku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Deku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep seeing more\Nand more amazing sides to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During the cavalry battle, I thought\Nit'd be easier to team up with friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now that I think about it,\NI might've been trying to rely on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, when Iida said he'd challenge you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it actually made me feel a little embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uraraka...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's facing the future\Nand trying their hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means we're all rivals, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet in the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two guys with the same Quirks!\NTetsutetsu versus Kirishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A head-to-head fistfight! The winner is--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both contestants down! It's a draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the case of a draw, after they recover,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the winner will be determined by\Na simple contest, like arm wrestling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their ability was the same, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like passionate guys like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're inspiring.\NI'd like a sidekick like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we wait for Tetsutetsu\Nand Kirishima to recover,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll start the next match!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Katsuki Bakugo"     "Ochaco Uraraka"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next might be the most disturbing match-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost don't want to watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uraraka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The eighth and last match of the first round!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was kind of famous in middle school!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the face of a regular person!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the hero course, it's Katsuki Bakugo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Versus--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one I'm rooting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the hero course, it's Ochaco Uraraka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eighth match, start!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:22.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is, you know, the preview...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uraraka, there's no spirit in your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.01,0:23:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess that makes sense,\Nsince your first match is against Kacchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to become a hero\Nand let my parents take it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deku, let's meet in the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.44,0:23:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, good luck, Uraraka!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Bakugo vs. Uraraka"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.90,0:23:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The meteor shower falling from\Nthe sky will be the path to victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go beyond!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:51.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next time: Bakugo vs. Uraraka"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.34,0:23:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus Ultra!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.13,0:23:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.12,0:23:55.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
